      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(WeightValuePair<V> o)
        Compares two WeightValuePair objects in accordance with their weights in reversed order. This function is equivalent to Double.compare(o.getWeight, this.getWeight()).
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<WeightValuePair<V>>
        Parameters:
        o - the WeightValuePair object to be compared
        Returns:
        the value 0 if o.getWeight() is numerically equal to this.getWeight(); a value less than 0 if o.getWeight() is numerically less than this.getWeight(); and a value greater than 0 if o.getWeight() is numerically greater than this.getWeight().
